0:02:51.200,0:02:59.920
We believe that we can "open the light" to other people, to everybody.

0:02:59.920,0:03:01.340
It is wonderful.

0:03:01.340,0:03:04.180
We want you to keep it, Prophet.

0:03:04.180,0:03:05.380
Thank you very much.

0:03:05.380,0:03:07.920
This is your office in Jerusalem.

0:03:07.920,0:03:08.720
No problem.

