The Council was created in order to have open lines of communication between religious leaders

0:05:19.720,0:05:24.600
so that through good times and bad times and in crisis situations,

0:05:24.600,0:05:29.180
there is a possibility of communication to solve problems,

0:05:29.180,0:05:31.500
