0:05:31.500,0:05:36.000
It is all about love; God is love.

0:05:36.000,0:05:41.980
Like the Book of 1 Corinthians 13:13 says, the greatest is love.

0:05:41.980,0:05:46.620
Also in the Hebrew Bible, the love of God appears many more times than the fear of God.

0:05:46.620,0:05:48.140
Thank you.

0:05:48.140,0:05:50.420
Let us love one another.

0:05:50.420,0:05:56.480
God is love.
We must love one another.

