Love looks around to see who is in need, who is crying, who is unsafe.

0:06:13.640,0:06:15.420
That is love.

0:06:15.420,0:06:22.120
Failing to walk in love almost shuts down our spiritual walk with the Lord.

0:06:22.120,0:06:31.520
When I met Rabbi, I realised what he is doing in Jerusalem, Israel and all over the world

0:06:31.520,0:06:34.520
