0:06:34.520,0:06:38.980
I said we have to come together and see what we could do.

0:06:38.980,0:06:41.480
We cannot just look to the other side.

0:06:41.480,0:06:45.840
Prophet T.B. Joshua Arrives For A Meeting With Religious Leaders In Jerusalem

0:06:45.840,0:06:51.000
In his meeting with religious leaders from the Council of Religious Institutions of the Holy Land,

0:06:51.000,0:06:58.140
Prophet T.B. Joshua emphasizes on the importance of love, as the language that transcends all barriers

0:06:58.140,0:07:06.100
of race, religion, nationality and culture.

0:07:06.100,0:07:07.940
Love is the greatest.

0:07:07.940,0:07:13.600
If love is the greatest, there is nothing we can do without love.

0:07:13.600,0:07:17.600
All our efforts and attributes without love are nothing.

0:07:17.600,0:07:19.780
Thank you for coming.

0:07:19.780,0:07:22.740
