0:08:34.940,0:08:42.540
It is very interesting to know the person and hear about his unbelievable work.

0:08:42.540,0:08:47.400
It is an honour for us to meet such a great person.

0:08:47.400,0:08:51.440
Our job here is to promote peace and work together.

0:08:51.440,0:08:54.860
We would be honoured and glad to work together.

0:08:54.860,0:09:00.400
I am Trond Bakkevig; I am a priest of the Church of Norway, Lutheran Church.

0:09:00.400,0:09:07.900
I am here in Jerusalem because I am the Convener of The Council Of Religious Institutions Of The Holy Land.

0:09:07.900,0:09:13.340
The purpose of the Council is to bring the religious leaders of Jerusalem and the Holy Land together

0:09:13.340,0:09:17.780
