0:19:25.520,0:19:27.840
Prophet T.B. Joshua Visits The Holy Land And Journeys To Hebron

0:19:27.840,0:19:35.740
During his visit to the Holy Land, Prophet T.B. Joshua travels south of Jerusalem to the cave of the patriarchs,

0:19:35.740,0:19:42.140
the tomb of Abraham, Isaac and Jacob in Hebron, ancient Judea.

0:19:42.140,0:19:50.940
As recorded in Genesis 23, "Afterward, Abraham buried his wife Sarah in the cave in the field of Machpelah

0:19:50.940,0:19:56.520
near Mamre (which is at Hebron) in the land of Canaan".

0:19:56.520,0:20:00.400
This is the visit of Prophet T.B. Joshua.

0:20:00.400,0:20:02.820
Welcome.

0:20:02.820,0:20:05.700
Abraham buried his wife Sarah here.

0:20:05.700,0:20:07.920
Why did Abraham bury his wife Sarah here?

0:20:07.920,0:20:11.260
He bought this from Ephron.

0:20:11.260,0:20:13.060
Why did he buy this place?

0:20:13.060,0:20:17.400
Because he knew that Adam and Eve were buried over here as well.

0:20:17.400,0:20:19.980
Prophet T.B. Joshua Visits Cave Of The Patriarchs - The Tomb Of Abraham, Isaac And Jacob In Hebron

0:20:19.980,0:20:28.060
As recorded in Genesis 25, "Then Abraham breathed his last and died at a good old age,

0:20:28.060,0:20:32.380
an old man and full of years".

0:20:32.380,0:20:38.340
His sons, Isaac and Ishmael, buried him in the Cave of Machpelah near Mamre.

0:20:38.340,0:20:42.960
There Abraham was buried with his wife Sarah.

0:20:42.960,0:20:52.740
Above this big structure, there is a church from the time of the Crusaders which was built on top of this structure.

0:20:52.740,0:20:56.020
Prophet T.B. Joshua Visits Cave Of The Patriarchs - The Tomb Of Abraham, Isaac And Jacob In Hebron

0:20:56.020,0:20:58.040
This is the Seventh Step.

0:20:58.040,0:21:02.600
Prophet T.B. Joshua Visits Cave Of The Patriarchs - The Tomb Of Abraham, Isaac And Jacob In Hebron

0:21:02.600,0:21:06.900
The Jews used to come to the Seventh Step, which is over here.

0:21:06.900,0:21:13.860
Today, thank God, since we liberated in 1967, we can enter the cave.

0:21:13.860,0:21:16.820
Prophet T.B. Joshua Visits Cave Of The Patriarchs - The Tomb Of Abraham, Isaac And Jacob In Hebron

0:21:16.820,0:21:24.460
When we speak about the actual graves, you have to understand they are three stories down.

0:21:24.460,0:21:33.320
Herod built this structure; then the Turks, the Ottomans came and built this structure.

0:21:33.320,0:21:39.720
And because it is a holy place, they built two mosques on top.

0:21:39.720,0:21:51.280
And still today, we have a church on the roof which was built in the time of the Crusaders.

